cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.DC 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper focuses on integrating deep learning based computer vision algorithms with low-resource devices, which falls under the scope of computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of deep learning algorithms, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
3. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper presents a Raspberry Pi based robot, Cloud Chaser, to demonstrate the power of using cloud computing for real-time vision tasks. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper discusses the use of deep learning algorithms, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper proposes offloading computation work to the cloud, which falls under the scope of distributed computing.
